{"tid":1356133,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《過份》深水埗連儂隧道有人踩場，黑警又想放人","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:54:32.000Z","uid":283617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e0be3fec4d0e1e3d50969fd9d86739c20017da","tid":1356133,"uid":283617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"頭先6點半左右 係深水埗元州街45號往石硤尾方向 有2個男人撕紙 其實撕最多係藍衫男人 過程中有電訊盈科員工叫佢唔好整到佢地做嘢d宣傳poster 然後藍衫男人就發惡咁反擊 仲打電話去電訊盈科想投訴個員工 之後有人就報警 原因係藍衫男人將d紙丟到成個隧道都係 仲差d搞到路過既婆婆跌親 5分鐘後警察到場 要求佢清理返地下d紙 <br />\n而PC12573 似係有心想幫藍衫男人 叫佢下次再撕紙 如果有人打佢就報警 會幫佢拉哂其他人 事實上當時無任何人出手打人 <br />\n到最後係藍衫男人邊繼續撕紙邊執地上既紙既時候 有兩個男人 粉紅色衫同佢朋友 兩個廢老突然鬧我地 話乜撚嘢民主 話我地阻住哂 累死d警察 粉紅色男人仲一度行到好前想打人咁 最後警察拉走兩個廢老 <br />\n希望係隧道起場既同路人 呢幾日一齊去整返好 因為大部份紙都比佢撕走<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG1A1uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG1A1uv.jpg&h=28d08123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpHpanR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpHpanR.jpg&h=59652ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG1A1ux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG1A1ux.jpg&h=3d5a9311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRsXvnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRsXvnU.jpg&h=49ff9d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaaumuA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaaumuA.jpg&h=02a61638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8PiZgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8PiZgg.jpg&h=f3eb1839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5gYePC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5gYePC.jpg&h=019cfbd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hypCvnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhyp